data.description: An incredible opportunity to own over 5 acres in the Wellington equestrian district  for under $2m! ThIs well engineered 3 bedroom, 3.2 bathroom plus bonus room home has already undergone a considerable renovation including a new kitchen, floors, bathrooms, light fixtures, pool decking and more. The Primary suite is large with cabana french doors and a spacious walk through closet. Volume ceilings throughout. The exterior boasts a freshly painted 3 stall barn with a tack room, new horse fencing around the entire property, paddocks, a new driveway, new electronic property gate, and new landscaping are just a few of the recent upgrades. (Please see Supplemental Information and walk through video). This property has access to the lovely Little Ranches horse trails. Covered arenas permitted.
